 command will search the repository for the specified chart and display all available versions, including pre-release and deprecated versions, with the latest version listed first. The \"--devel\" flag is used to include pre-release versions in the search results. The \"--sort date\" flag is used to sort the results by time, with the most recent version listed first."}]